    <item>
      <title>Re: Tradeskill Tests new requirement?</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Trade&amp;message.id=12234#M12234</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I specifically Chose west freeport because.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;#1 As mentioned, there are not really any safe areas in the expansion zones.&amp;nbsp; Even if seemingly safe, there are still "train" problems.&amp;nbsp; In Freeport you ate least have the opportunity to get faction to the point where you can mostly ignore trains.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;#2 it did not make sense to me to have them in those zones, at least not story wise.&amp;nbsp; Though I probably could have twisted something around for it.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;#3 Freeport was being revamped.&amp;nbsp; I wanted something to bring people there.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;#4 They were adding faction quests to easily get to at least dubious in freeport, and with not too much work, friendly enough to buy.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;#5 I did not want to add yet MORE NPC's to Plane of Knowledge.&amp;nbsp; It is already crowded there.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;#6 when I made the decision, and added the NPC and had already implemented the 1300 database entries required for the tasks, and the 400 or so lines of script necessary to work with trophies, being a new designer... I did not even think about the Expansion only requirement.&amp;nbsp; As I have said before... I agree at the same time as disagree with the decision to restrict this to Expansion only.&amp;nbsp; I decided It was fine where it was.&amp;nbsp; Plus it would have taken alot of work to then move the NPC's.&amp;nbsp; Call me lazy if you want, but I was also under heavy time constraints and had alot of other work to do.&amp;nbsp; I made the decision that it would have the same problem in PoK, and as #1 says, there was no good place to put it in the expansion zones for lower level characters.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;So while the decision to make it expansion only was not mine, I do not want you thinking the choice of the placement was anything but my decision, and that I did consider moving them, but decided against it.&amp;nbsp; I also want to be clear that I agree with the decision to make it expansion only, even if I may not like it.&amp;nbsp; Sometimes a choice has to be made whether I like it or not :) We need to make money on the expansions, and we need to put in it things that players want, or we will not get money from the expansion.&amp;nbsp; With that in mind, we cannot just freely give it out then, if we want to make money from it.&amp;nbsp; Again there is that fact that we are a business.&amp;nbsp; I love tradeskills, but I definitely want to be paid for doing this job, I am not quite so magnanimous as to do this much work for free :)&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Dev-Ngreth on &lt;span class=date_text&gt;03-29-2006&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=time_text&gt;10:18 AM&lt;/span&gt;</description>
